, API, library, class', 'CleanTalk Anti-Spam Installation Manuals', '2018-02-08 14:48:52', NULL, NULL),
(267, 361, 'help', 'Инструкции по установке антиспама от CleanTalk', '<h1 style="text-align: center;">Инструкции по установке антиспама от CleanTalk</h1>\n<h3>Здесь находятся&nbsp;инструкции по установке антиспама для популярных CMS.</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Антиспам:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src="../images/wordpress.ico" alt="WordPress" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=wordpress">WordPress</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/joomla15.ico" alt="Joomla" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=joomla3">Joomla 2.x-3.x</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/joomla15.ico" alt="Joomla" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=joomla15">Joomla 1.5</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/phpbb31.ico" alt="phpBB 3.1" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=phpbb31">phpBB 3.1, 3.2</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/phpbb3.ico" alt="phpBB 3" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=phpbb3">phpBB 3.0</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/smf.ico" alt="Simple Machines Forum" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=smf">Simple Machines Forum</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/xenforo.ico" alt="XenForo" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=xenforo">XenForo</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/xenforo.ico" alt="Xenforo2" width="16" height="16" /> <a href="/install?platform=xenforo2">XenForo 2.x</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/ipboard4.ico" alt="IPS Community Suite 4" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=ipboard4">IPS Community Suite 4</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/ipboard.ico" alt="IP.Board" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=ipboard">IP.Board</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/drupal.ico" alt="Drupal" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=drupal">Drupal 7</a></li>\n<li><img src="../images/drupal8.ico" alt="Drupal 8" width="16" height="16" />&nbsp;<a href="/install?platform=drupal8">Drupal 8</a></li>\n<li><i